          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1615218111348-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once browned, add the <strong>beef stock</strong>,<strong> grated carrot</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to the beef mince<strong> </strong>and cook for 8-10 min or until thickened – this is your <strong>lean</strong> <strong>ragù</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1615218116094-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1615218116094-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1615218116094-x700.jpg",
