          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1615218119933-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>macaroni</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> to the <strong>béchamel</strong> and mix well – this is your <strong>macaroni cheese</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>lean</strong> <strong>ragù </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>(or individual smaller ones!) and top with the <strong>macaroni cheese</strong></p><p>Sprinkle the<strong> grated cheese </strong>over the top and put the dish in the oven for 15 min or until bubbling and golden – this is your<strong> lean ragù bake</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
