            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash the <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with <strong>kitchen paper</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> remaining balsamic vinegar </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and toss through the <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>lean</strong> <strong>ragù bake</strong> with the <strong>dressed salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
